00:01:55.914 --> 00:02:00.974
What we’re going to do in today’s episode is first define exactly what it

00:02:00.974 --> 00:02:08.444
is, how it works, where this idea originated from, how the events of 2020

00:02:08.454 --> 00:02:13.804
have changed public perceptions towards it, and why it’s the United States,

